<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Hikayemiz | Budva Cafe</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@700&family=Inter:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">

    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            color: #4a4a4a;
        }
        
        .hero-header {
            background-color: #8da399;
            height: 250px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .back-btn {
            position: absolute;
            top: 25px;
            left: 30px;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 16px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            transition: opacity 0.3s;
        }
        
        .back-btn:hover {
            opacity: 0.8;
        }
        
        .content-card {
            background: white;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: -80px auto 50px;
            padding: 50px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            padding-top: 80px;
        }
        
        .logo-container {
            width: 180px;
            height: 180px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 50%;
            padding: 0;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15) display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            overflow: hidden;
            position: absolute;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            top: -90px;
        }
        
        .logo-img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }
        
        h1.page-title {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            color: #2c3e50;
            font-size: 32px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        
        .subtitle {
            color: #8da399;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            display: block;
        }
        
        p.story-text {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .info-grid {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 40px;
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding-top: 30px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        
        .info-item {
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .info-item i {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #8da399;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .info-item span {
            display: block;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #333;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="hero-header">
        <a href="/" class="back-btn">
            <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i> Ana Sayfa
        </a>
    </div>

    <div class="content-card">

        <div class="logo-container">
            <img src="/img/logo.png" alt="Budva Cafe Logo" class="logo-img">
        </div>

        <h1 class="page-title">Hikayemiz</h1>

        <p class="story-text">
            Merhaba, biz <strong>Budva Cafe!</strong>
        </p>
        <p class="story-text">
            Karadağ'ın sakinliğinden ve doğallığından ilham alarak kurduğumuz cafemizde, en taze kahve çekirdeklerini ve sıcak lezzetleri sizlerle buluşturuyoruz.
        </p>
        <p class="story-text">
            Amacımız sadece bir kahve sunmak değil; günün yorgunluğunu atabileceğiniz, dostlarınızla keyifli vakit geçirebileceğiniz sıcak bir yuva olmak. Her sabah fırından yeni çıkan kruvasan kokusuyla güne başlayıp gecenin ilerleyen saatlerine kadar en samimi
            sohbetlerinize eşlik ediyoruz.
        </p>

        <div class="info-grid">
            <div class="info-item">
                <i class="far fa-clock"></i>
                <span>Her Gün: 10:00 - 00:00</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-item">
                <i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i>
                <span>Bayrampaşa / İstanbul</span>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

</body>

</html>